➜广西诗人陈熠明：遥远了天涯的过往
http://www.sohu.com/a/425550294_100115135	33950
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201018/0db2d289165f4d15a73a50808065e190.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遥远了天涯的过往</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>现代诗原创作品·心灵诗幻陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(一)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时光摇晃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摇晃着你的影子走过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>走过了阳光里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个灼热了岁月的远方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悬挂在云霞高处的眼光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在清风徐来的天涯里悠悠地飘荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘荡着你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心缠绵了情感的流浪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流浪过云霞的身旁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你看到云霞里静静地灿烂着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>灿烂着那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>光明了世界的太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从来不想让</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自己的脚步迷茫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>迷茫在轮回里那一程</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>辗转了岁月和辗转了时光的过往</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(二)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春风激荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">激荡着你的心花盛开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>盛开起时光里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个漫长了思念的芬芳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晾晒在心河岸上的霞光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在春风习来的天地里柔柔地飘荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘荡着你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一园弥漫了热恋的花香</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漂泊过流水的岸上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你看到碧波里悠悠地荡漾着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>荡漾着那一心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>炫丽了眼眸的阳光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从来不想让</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自己的影子彷徨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>彷徨在等远里那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>向往了真心和向往了真爱的梦想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(三)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总有一心向往</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牵引着你的脚步走向</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>走向着重逢里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个花开了岁月的芬芳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">痴情鸟在枝头用他一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦幻了时光的歌喉在婉转地歌唱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>歌唱着高亢里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个风动了云外的太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天涯里那一只</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扶摇直上的红鹰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>正在胸怀坦荡的高空里大展</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>大展着他一双飞越过了天涯的翅膀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">转身的时候你看见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看见那一片重新灿烂起了生命的霞光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201018/c6dfe26b0f7b4c56b2bfb103adc523c8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(四)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>总有一情幻想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>牵引着你的目光遥望</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥望着归来里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一张微笑着流年的脸庞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>痴情鸟在云边用他一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>坦荡了时光的翅膀在浪漫地飞向</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飞向着流云里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心感动了青天的月亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天涯里那一只</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>潇洒远去的红船</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正在胸怀广阔的大海里向往</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">向往着他一心打捞过了天涯的情网</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>回头的时候你看见</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>看见那一片重新璀璨起了生命的星光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(五)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘落在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阴霾里的影子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>渐渐地迷失去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>迷失去你那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>痴情了热恋的远航</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阴霾本来就不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不知道影子那颗痴心在流血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>流血着你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一情撕裂了疼痛的悲伤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">撒开了思念的情网</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在那一场梦的心海里却打捞不出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打捞不出</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个再来了相逢的梦想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(六)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人海茫茫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天涯路茫茫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一颗心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>总是错觉地认为</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">认为只要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一路努力地去追寻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一个人自己</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就可以寻找得到</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寻找得到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一个诗情了画意的远方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>其实不然</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>因为追寻的路上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有些时候是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相遇着漫长的黑暗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有些时候啊是相遇着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>相遇着那一个光明了磊落的太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201018/5331f4f6a3214c14826ecfea6aff01a8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(七)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘落在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黑夜里的花朵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>渐渐地退隐去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>退隐去你那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>痴情了情感的芬芳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黑夜本来就不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不知道花朵那片嘴唇在流血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>流血着你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一情别离了落寞的惆怅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">洒下了思念的月光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在那一场梦的尘世里却明朗不出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>明朗不出</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个再来了重逢的希望</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(八)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云海茫茫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尘世路茫茫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一颗心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>总是幻觉地认定</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">认定只要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一路风雨地去追寻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一个人自己</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就可以寻找得到</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寻找得到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心点燃了生命的曙光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>其实不然</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>因为追寻的路上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有些时候是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相遇着风霜的迷茫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有些时候啊是相遇着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>相遇着那一个祥和了善念的月亮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(九)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你在清风里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将思念化成酸涩的泪水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>反反</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>复复地去湿润着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">湿润着心灵深处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一些﻿干枯了岁月的诗行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你不想去读懂远方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也不想再去明白远方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为你已不再渴望着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">渴望着让那一些不理解你的过往</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在撕开了岁月的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>伤口触痛起你前尘的创伤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">停留在十字路口的目光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">突然在行驶的规则里失去了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">失去了他的使唤和失去了他的朝向</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>干脆向着梦里吧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也许在梦幻最宁静的地方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你会找到了归宿里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一个全方位地锁定了目标的远航</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201018/d5001b7259024f038600c15dd64ef983.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你在明月处</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>将牵挂化成血泪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">往往地去湿润着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>湿润着心灵深处</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一些苦涩了年华的诗行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你不想去乞求远方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不想再去巴结远方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>因为你已不再等望着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>等望着让那一些不明白你的诽谤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在裂开了岁月的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伤口触痛起你难言的悲伤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>停留在岁月云边的脚步</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>突然在前程的攀登里失去了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>失去了他的思路和失去了他的向往</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">干脆向着梦里吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也许在梦幻最广阔的地方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你会找到了追寻里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个全方位地锁定了情感的梦想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十一)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多少个被尘埃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">封存了千年的渴望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>再也走不出</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心锁定了千年的洪荒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被心血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">渲染过的太阳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在黎明的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>云霞里纷纷扬扬地飘荡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘荡着梦想里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一张轮回了前世的脸庞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>用心血凝成的祈祷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在通往彼岸的心海里辗转激荡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">激荡起那一浪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高过了诺言的说谎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>好想彻底遗忘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>好想用一心梦幻来彻底遗忘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遗忘着岁月里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一眼失落了光明的忧伤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可自古</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>以来有谁可以</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有谁可以用谎言骗过了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">骗过了自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一个年少起岁月的轻狂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201018/1a77944d3e3d4161abf4a13535245212.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十三)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>多少个被欲望</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>封存了千年的翅膀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再也飞不出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心淹没了千年的过往</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>被眼泪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>潮湿过的月亮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在暮晚的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流云里遥遥远远地飘荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘荡着梦境里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一眸穿越了前尘的眼光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十四)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用心血烧开的祝福</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在通往未来的桃源里辗转怒放</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>怒放出那一片</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>赛过了诺言的芬芳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好想彻底遗忘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好想用一心感慨来彻底遗忘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遗忘着时空里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一脸干枯了喜悦的惆怅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可自古</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以来有谁能够</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有谁能够用虚伪骗过了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>骗过了自己</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个年少起人海的潮浪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十五)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仰望着夜空里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一弯刚刚升起的月亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也不知道是谁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>用那一言讥笑膨胀了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">膨胀了你肩膀上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一个沉重了泪雨的行囊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>祝福里带着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>妒忌而来的潮浪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总想在你那一船</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远航还没到达的彼岸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>熙熙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>攘攘地闹醒了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闹醒了那一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本来就该﻿属于你自己的梦想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201018/f7002eeea8cd412ab333523f695c7b99.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十六)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>痴情花的芬芳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>红红火火地淹没过</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">淹没过岁月边那一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">淡淡地说走了青春的渴望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悬挂于枝头里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一片惹火了热恋的春光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正在顺着远去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的流水羞羞答答地流淌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流淌向下一个那轮回了生命的远方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>桃花渡口</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心兰舟的启航</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在黎明绚丽的云霞里载走了你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">载走了你相思里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一晨温暖地灿烂了春华的曙光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十七)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遥望着天涯里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个即将升起的太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不知道是谁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用那一言嘲讽打落了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打落了你枝头上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一首潮湿了泪雨的诗行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">羡慕里带着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妒忌而来的风向</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>总想在你那一场</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>花开还没醒来的远方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纷纷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扰扰地吵醒了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吵醒了那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>本来就该属于你自己的梦乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十八)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">痴情花的梦想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">深深浅浅地芳菲过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>芳菲过时光里那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悄悄地说走了轻年的模样</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隐藏在花开里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片激活了热恋的疯狂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>正在顺着远去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>的春风纷纷扬扬地飘荡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘荡于下一个那冲动了灵魂的梦乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白云山边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一只凤凰的飞翔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在黎明欢笑的彩霞里带走了你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>带走了你牵挂里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心灼热地滚烫了时光的太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201018/a5520dc36f9343188696123200a87c99.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201018/a4162f921e484a959e92eb70ed4792ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
<p>★ <strong>名誉社长:</strong>叶仲录 ☆<strong>总顾问:</strong>薛依云 ☆<strong>首席顾问:</strong>欧大象 ☆<strong>执行顾问:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>顾问团成员:</strong>欧大象（文光）、岩心（薛莹）、石秉旺、陈文化、高原红、碧海（陈碧珍)、黄香玉 ☆<strong>社长兼总编:</strong>星连 ☆<strong>常务副社长:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>副社长:</strong>丁冬亮、绝尘道长、梁继权、高晓园、陈熠明、东晓 、木子 ☆<strong>艺术总监:</strong>陆廷教 ☆<strong>编委会主任:</strong>听尘居士 ☆<strong>编委会成员:</strong>孤客、黄香玉、星连、枫叶、绮雯、徐玉兰、叶仲录、薛依云、高晓园、田书芹、木子……（添加中） ☆<strong>主编:</strong>游散居士 ☆<strong>副主编：</strong> 丁冬亮、闫加辉、张立标、张君霞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201018/b4989fd18a0f4ab89e7f472710826f6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201018/e90370ed5ae64bdb87f09c480fe730da.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖主编简介：</strong></p>
<p>▲笔名：星连、星连193，原名：卢链生，号游散居士，别号：中原听真，男，汉族，七零后，籍贯：广东汕尾，现居深圳。系中国诗联协会理事，中国诗词协会会员，世界汉诗协会会员，中国网络诗歌学会会员，河北采风学会会员，中原诗词研究会会员，太行诗词协会会员，认证诗人，网站签约作家。2014年受江西电台连线采访，作品散发各大网站及入选各类诗集、文集等，诗歌及其他作品曾获特等奖、一等奖、二等奖、铜奖、优秀奖各类奖项。主要结集作品有：诗集《爱情与人生》，长篇小说《漂泊》、《江湖客传》、《都市迷情之情仇恩怨》，小说集《百味人生》以及散文集等。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201018/cfae99b3107f4fa3b1926a401c1e5089.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖郑重声明:</strong></p>
<p><strong>1.来稿必须原创作品，所有来稿投稿者文责自负，一切纠纷与本平台无关。</strong></p>
