➜苏坛：《有趣的灵魂》
http://www.sohu.com/a/425551270_100115135	34246
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201018/1c236d851e94418caffc41843fc0f9ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《有趣的灵魂》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黑夜降临以后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有趣的灵魂会傻傻地聚在一起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一位带眼镜的女士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她总是那么优雅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为我们沏茶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>他们会讨论一下小人物</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一位老师说</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我们只能在残疾人身上找到善良</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>清风如徐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>审美才是艺术的境界</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我想走进作者的内心世界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">探求一个密码</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">批评与赞美同在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阅读是有声音的撞击</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人制止我的发言</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>用诗句来总结一下评论</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
